{
  "texts": [
    "A close match indicates that ENMA has learned to infer physically consistent initial conditions and dynamics from context.",
    "As shown in fig. 23, the trajectories produced by ENMA closely match those from the solver, both qualitatively and quantitatively.",
    "We also report a relative L2 error of 0.081 between the AVIT 4.26e-2 1.68e-1 1.57e-1 5.88e-1 1.76e-1 3.77e-1 Zebra 4.21e-2 1.82e-1 1.40e-1 3.15e-1 4.43e-2 2.23e-1 ENMA 2.23e-2 1.52e-1 7.00e-2 2.83e-1 5.21e-2 2.82e-1 closely matching Zebra.",
    "These results highlight ENMA's strong predictive performance under comparable constraints.",
    "One of the primary limitations of generative models compared to deterministic surrogates lies in their inference speed."
  ]
}